Class Mission

java.lang.Object
model.mission.Mission
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Mission>
public class Mission extends Object implements Comparable<Mission>
This class provides a Mission, made of one or multiple steps, and multiple endings.

      Main constructor for Mission.
      Parameters:
      id - The Mission ID.
      name - The Mission name.
      steps - The Step(s) this mission has.
      neededPoints - The Mission needed points.
      attributeRequirements - The Mission needed requirements, in terms of a name associated with its value.
      issueDateTime - The Mission creation date and time.
      endings - A Set of final effects applied at the end of the Mission.
